{"tid":914953,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"人生就好似飲食","createTime":"2018-11-24T16:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T08:44:37.000Z","uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25f91f8a9e1976aacca7b86373276b620d3ed392","tid":914953,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"甜 酸 苦 辣<br />\n甜 同人快樂時光<br />\n酸 又被前面對情侶閃盲了<br />\n苦 唉 又失戀了<br />\n辣 果個真係仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n人生就係因為呢4種味道 <br />\n生活先有色彩<br />\n咁樣就一個月了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/000158_d95dde9b0b115333ed168e9a95a05380.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F000158_d95dde9b0b115333ed168e9a95a05380.png&h=4315600d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾日晚餐 <br />\n峰味 四種味都食唔出<br />\n<br />\n當人生失去味覺<br />\n話下來 只係為左生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8cc675b0ffa34bfa49663378d1a769f0a5c674","tid":914953,"uid":124824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"第5種味係尷尬"}]}